{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d135050b3c","title":"接见谢富治同志时的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6e0b69e537","index":0,"year":1967,"month":4,"day":19,"articleId":"d135050b3c"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1961-1968卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9cc7c0932c","type":"title","text":"接见谢富治同志时的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"d135050b3c"},{"id":"b07d6a6e32","type":"paragraph","text":"我祝贺你，祝贺这次大会的成功。请代向全北京市革命造反派祝贺。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"d135050b3c"},{"id":"c4f9afafe5","type":"paragraph","text":"致敬电是全世界无产者联合起来的大宣言，就不要再搞宣言了。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"d135050b3c"},{"id":"5d4e752684","type":"paragraph","text":"青年人要参加你们的工作，使前辈人不脱离群众，使青年人得到锻炼。青年人不能脱产，这样会造成脱离群众的，要半官半民。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"d135050b3c"},{"id":"aac6b4dcd2","type":"paragraph","text":"北京的形势还有反复，无政府主义就是机会主义的惩罚。要不怕犯错误，各种反动的观点和反动的群众组织是极少数的。就是反动组织也要做工作，但是还得斗争。","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"d135050b3c"}],"page":{"id":"ead6983135","publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"d135050b3c","start":581,"end":581}}}},"__N_SSG":true}